quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  4,66,"Hara nun Men Farluno e ma…ď…ďe nde yoga ma…ď…ďe warata yoga, maa yaltugol e galleeji ma…ď…ďe …óin ; ko see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe wa…óaynoo …óum. Yo …ďe yettude Alla tawnoo O Fawaali …ďe ko …ďe townataa. Sinno …ďe wa…óuno ko …ďe yamiraa e …óoftagol Alla, …óum laatotono mo∆ī∆īere, e ko …ďurata tii…óude e tabital liimanaaku, Men Ye…óayno …ďe kadi baraaji maw…ói, Men Fewnira …ďe laawol Alla ngol e Aljanna Makko on :"
  4,67,"Hara nun Men Farluno e ma…ď…ďe nde yoga ma…ď…ďe warata yoga, maa yaltugol e galleeji ma…ď…ďe …óin ; ko see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe wa…óaynoo …óum. Yo …ďe yettude Alla tawnoo O Fawaali …ďe ko …ďe townataa. Sinno …ďe wa…óuno ko …ďe yamiraa e …óoftagol Alla, …óum laatotono mo∆ī∆īere, e ko …ďurata tii…óude e tabital liimanaaku, Men Ye…óayno …ďe kadi baraaji maw…ói, Men Fewnira …ďe laawol Alla ngol e Aljanna Makko on."
  4,68,"4:67"
  4,69,"Kala on …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo on : on …óon wonndoyay e …ďen …ďe Alla Neeminiri naatugol Aljanna immorde e Annabaa…ďe, e goongu…ďe e ko Nulaa…ďe …ďen addi kon …ďe gollitiri …óum, e sahodin…ďe fii laawol diina Alla, e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe mo∆ī∆īini golle-mun. ∆Āen …óon mo∆ī∆īii wonndii…ďe ka Aljanna !"
  4,70,"Ndin mbarjaari jaŇčtaandi …óon ko ∆Āural ngal Alla Hertinani jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Alla Yonii Anndu…óo fiyakuuji mon, O Yo…ďitoyay kala e golle mun !"
  4,71,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, ∆īettee reŇčtor…ói mon …óin jogito…óon ko da…óitoron e ay…ďe …ďen si hare yanii, yaltiron e ma…ď…ďe konu konu, maa yaltiron on denndaangal ; no gasiraŇčta on woo mettinirangol ay…ďe mon …ďen."
  4,72,"Hino e mo'on onon juul…ďe …ďen, yim…ďe nennotoo…ďe yahugol ha…ďa ay…ďe mon …ďen sabu kulol reedu, …ďe nenna kadi wo…ď…ďe goo ; …ďen le ko naafiqi en. Si on waraama maa on foolaama, go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe weltora wi'ugol: "Gom…óii Alla Mo∆ī∆īike e am, mi tawdaaka e ma…ď…ďe sakko musiiba he…ďida lam e ma…ď…ďe"."
  4,73,"Si tawii le ∆Āural foolugol maa he…ďugol honateeri he…ďii onon juul…ďe …ďen immorde ka Alla, on nennii…óo e jihaadi ndin wowliray wa si tawiino giggol laatanooki hakkunde mon e makko : "Ee jalla am sinno mi laatoduno e ma…ď…ďe ka hare, mi he…ďii ∆Āural ngal …ďe he…ďi !"."
  4,74,"Yo gom…óim…ďe …ďen ha…ďu fii Alla no Konngol Alla ngol …ďamtora, …ďen goongu…ďe soodiroo…ďe nguur-aduna fii laakara. Kala on ha…ďidaa…óo fii laawol Alla ngol no …ďamtora o sahodini, maa o fooli ga√Īo on, arma Alla Okka mo njo…ďdi mawndi ; ko ndin woni Aljanna e Welayee Alla."